ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I would recommend Painting Photography Film to another student, if they are interested in art and medium theory.
A great class in the department to take.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Yes, this course has been helpful for my thesis preparation.

I was writing a paper on copyright law so it was great! It also helped sharpen some of my other papers I was writing on moral rights law. A class outside the law school that is actually rigorous inits readings and discussion versus just a free-for-all is super helpful.
